move.label: move
move.documentation: This function makes karel move forward one space.

turnLeft.label: turnLeft
turnLeft.documentation: This function makes karel turn left.

pickBeeper.label: pickBeeper
pickBeeper.documentation: This function makes karel pick up a beeper.

putBeeper.label: putBeeper
putBeeper.documentation: This function makes karel put down a beeper.

frontIsClear.label: frontIsClear
frontIsClear.documentation: This function returns true if there is no wall in front of karel.

leftIsClear.label: leftIsClear
leftIsClear.documentation: This function returns true if there is no wall to the left of karel.

rightIsClear.label: rightIsClear
rightIsClear.documentation: This function returns true if there is no wall to the right of karel.

frontIsBlocked.label: frontIsBlocked
frontIsBlocked.documentation: This function returns true if there is a wall in front of karel.

leftIsBlocked.label: leftIsBlocked
leftIsBlocked.documentation: This function returns true if there is a wall to the left of karel.

rightIsBlocked.label: rightIsBlocked
rightIsBlocked.documentation: This function returns true if there is a wall to the right of karel.

beepersPresent.label: beepersPresent
beepersPresent.documentation: This function returns true if there is a beeper on the current space.

noBeepersPresent.label: noBeepersPresent
noBeepersPresent.documentation: This function returns true if there is no beeper on the current space.

facingNorth.label: facingNorth
facingNorth.documentation: This function returns true if karel is facing north.

facingSouth.label: facingSouth
facingSouth.documentation: This function returns true if karel is facing south.

facingEast.label: facingEast
facingEast.documentation: This function returns true if karel is facing east.

facingWest.label: facingWest
facingWest.documentation: This function returns true if karel is facing west.

notFacingNorth.label: notFacingNorth
notFacingNorth.documentation: This function returns true if karel is not facing north.

notFacingSouth.label: notFacingSouth
notFacingSouth.documentation: This function returns true if karel is not facing south.

notFacingEast.label: notFacingEast
notFacingEast.documentation: This function returns true if karel is not facing east.

notFacingWest.label: notFacingWest
notFacingWest.documentation: This function returns true if karel is not facing west.
